## Additional Context

This is a 2-founder startup. The CEO is also the technical founder, so the CPO should be highly autonomous (Tier 1 for most decisions). The sales lead (Anna) is non-technical — all outputs to her must go through Slack in a human-readable format.

The Bubble.io API is the primary data source. API credentials are stored at ~/.config/customer-monitoring/credentials.json.

Finnish business hours apply (Helsinki timezone). Expect lower activity in July (summer break) and during Christmas.
